#JP\">\n                <ab>\n                    <lb n=\"1\"/><expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <g ref=\"#interpunct\">·</g> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <g ref=\"#interpunct\">·</g>\n                    <lb n=\"2\"/><persName type=\"attested\"><name>Calbentius</name> <name>Motho</name></persName> <g ref=\"#interpunct\">·</g> <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <g ref=\"#interpunct\">·</g>\n                    <lb n=\"3\"/>annos <g ref=\"#interpunct\">·</g> <num value=\"40\">XXXX</num> <g ref=\"#interpunct\">·</g> <persName type=\"attested\"><name>Calbentia</name> <g ref=\"#ivy-leaf\">❦</g>\n                    <lb n=\"4\"/><name>Fortunata</name></persName> <g ref=\"#interpunct\">·</g> fratri <g ref=\"#ivy-leaf\">❦</g>\n                    <lb n=\"5\"/>suo <g ref=\"#ivy-leaf\">❦</g> fecit <g ref=\"#ivy-leaf\">❦</g>\n                </ab>\n             </div>\n            <div type=\"apparatus\">\n               <listApp><app><note>Text based on autopsy</note></app></listApp>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                <p>To the shades of the underworld. Calbentius Motho lived for 40 years. Calbentia Fortunata made (this)\n                    for her brother</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\">\n                <p>Agli dei Mani. Calbentius Motho visse 40 anni, Calbentia Fortunata dedicò (questa iscrizione) a suo fratello</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"commentary\">\n                <p/>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"bibliography\">\n                <listBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        <citedRange>\n                            <ref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650772\">10.7193</ref>\n                        </citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\